result.deskripsine: With this add-on add the characters from the Friday Night Funkin video game to your Minecraft.\n\nIn which they will attack using their singing abilities, some will drop items and others are possible to make your friends in your Minecraft survival.

Take your characters from your favorite video game to the world of Minecraft.\n\nCreating a fun world together with your friends and acquaintances, this skin pack has everything you could wish for a fun time<

This is the newest recreation of Freddy Fazbear’s Pizza on his Minecraft Pe! Enjoy this amazing map, with custom textures, items, animatronics and mobs! Play with your friends and unravel the mysteries and Easter eggs behind this haunted Pizzeria!

By: Pedrinho1799

This is A Recreation of Freddy Fazbear’s Pizza a recreation of the second game of the Five Nights at Freddy’s horror franchise. What makes everything cool and chilling is the custom textures. Bring all the Animatronics, objects and things from the game universe to your Minecraft Pe. Explore and have fun with your friends on this amazing map!

This is an incredible recreation of the famous horror game Five Nights at Freddy’s. This map is a recreation of the fourth game of the Franchise. It is an amazing map with very realistic textures, which makes everything more cool and terrifying. Explore and play with your friends on this amazing map !!!

By: Pedrinho1799

This map will let you play through the first night in a Minecraft version of Five Nights at Freddy’s: Sister Location. It’s considered a survival horror game but this Minecraft version is probably way less scary. However, it does have many cool features such as a fully narrated story, custom sounds and other cool game mechanics. It’s a fairly short adventure but hopefully more nights will be added in the future.

By: DarkPower202

This is the second map in its series which lets you play through the second night of Five Nights at Freddy’s: Sister Location in Minecraft. Five Night of Freddy’s is one of the top horror games out there, so it’s really nice to see parts of it transformed into a Minecraft version. The map got some really nice game mechanics such as the narrated voice which will guide you through the adventure.

By: DarkPower202

This is the third installment of the popular recreation of Five Nights at Freddy’s: Sister Location in Minecraft. It’s a full-fledged adventure horror experience with approximately 10-15 minutes worth of gameplay. As usual, it’s very cool game mechanics such as a fully narrated story and custom textures.

By: DarkPower202

This map includes the two last parts (4 and 5) of the Popular Five Nights at Freddy’s: Sister Location recreation for Minecraft Bedrock Edition. The game mechanics great and include features like narrated voices and scary sounds. This combined with the custom textures help create a quite scary experience with the occasional surprises. If you enjoyed the previous maps then make sure to give this a try as well!

By: DarkPower202
